{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NCgoNgY4aE7TPHm44xKfRR","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! I have a complete picture of the shared crate. Here's my thorough exploration report:\n\n---\n\n## Shared Crate (`sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/`) — Complete Exploration\n\n### 1. Full File Listing\n\nThe shared crate contains 5 files total:\n\n```\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/\n├── Cargo.toml\n└── src/\n    ├── lib.rs\n    ├── constants.rs\n    ├── fees.rs\n    └── tiers.rs\n```\n\n### 2. `Cargo.toml` (Package Definition)\n\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/Cargo.toml`\n\n```toml\n[package]\nname = \"rng-shared\"\nversion = \"0.1.0\"\nedition = \"2021\"\n\n[dependencies]\nanchor-lang = { workspace = true }\n```\n\n**Key Details**:\n- Package name: `rng-shared`\n- Edition: 2021\n- Single dependency: `anchor-lang` (resolved from workspace)\n- No optional features defined\n- Pure library crate (no binary)\n\n### 3. `src/lib.rs` (Module Exports)\n\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/lib.rs`\n\n```rust\npub mod constants;\npub mod fees;\npub mod tiers;\n```\n\n**Key Details**:\n- Three public modules declared and re-exported\n- Each module is a single file in the `src/` directory\n- All modules are public (accessible from external crates that depend on `rng-shared`)\n\n### 4. `src/constants.rs` (Coin & Phase Constants)\n\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/constants.rs`\n\n**Public Constants**:\n- **Coin sides**: `SIDE_HEADS = 0`, `SIDE_TAILS = 1`\n- **Match phases**: \n  - `PHASE_WAITING = 0` — Creator placed bet, waiting for opponent\n  - `PHASE_LOCKED = 1` — Both players in, requesting VRF\n  - `PHASE_SETTLED = 2` — VRF resolved, winner determined\n  - `PHASE_CANCELLED = 3` — Creator cancelled before opponent joined\n- **Timeout**: `LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS = 120` (2 minutes)\n\n**Public Functions**:\n- `from_randomness(byte: u8) -> u8` — Derives a coin side (0 or 1) from randomness byte using modulo 2\n- `is_valid_side(side: u8) -> bool` — Validates if a side is HEADS (0) or TAILS (1)\n\n**Tests**: Full test coverage for both functions with edge cases (0, 1, 2, 255)\n\n### 5. `src/fees.rs` (Fee Calculation & Distribution)\n\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/fees.rs`\n\n**Public Constants** (Basis Points):\n- `TOTAL_FEE_BPS = 300` (3% total)\n- `REVENUE_BPS = 200` (200 bps — platform revenue)\n- `RAKEBACK_BPS = 70` (70 bps — rakeback/raid boss rewards pool)\n- `CHEST_BPS = 30` (30 bps — chest treasury)\n\n**Public Functions**:\n- `calculate_fee(amount: u64) -> u64` — Computes total fee in lamports: `(amount × 300) / 10,000`\n- `split_fee(fee: u64) -> (u64, u64, u64)` — Splits a fee amount into `(revenue, rakeback, chest)` tuple\n  - Uses proportional distribution based on bps constants\n  - Remainder goes to chest to avoid rounding loss\n\n**Tests**: Verification that fee calculations are correct and components sum to total\n\n**Example Calculations**:\n- 10,000 lamports → 300 lamports fee (3%)\n- Fee split: (200 rev, 70 rake, 30 chest)\n- 1,000,000 lamports → 30,000 lamports fee\n\n### 6. `src/tiers.rs` (Tier Entry Amounts)\n\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/tiers.rs`\n\n**Public Constant Arrays**:\n- `TIER_AMOUNTS: [u64; 6]` — Six fixed tier entry amounts in lamports:\n  - Index 0 (Iron): 5,000,000 (0.005 SOL)\n  - Index 1 (Bronze): 10,000,000 (0.01 SOL)\n  - Index 2 (Silver): 100,000,000 (0.1 SOL)\n  - Index 3 (Gold): 250,000,000 (0.25 SOL)\n  - Index 4 (Platinum): 500,000,000 (0.5 SOL)\n  - Index 5 (Diamond): 1,000,000,000 (1.0 SOL)\n- `TIER_COUNT: usize = 6`\n\n**Public Functions**:\n- `get_tier_amount(tier: u8) -> Result<u64>` — Safely retrieves tier amount or returns `TierError::InvalidTier`\n\n**Error Enum**:\n- `TierError` with error code discriminant